{"id":"01g8jrp6n2718942xggy7cdjt3","add_time_ms":1658487249570,"icon":"book","type":"doc","_id":"16","content":"　　在本章中，我们将介绍创建wxWidgets应用程序所需的基础知识。我们将创建一个简单的示例，展示如何显示一个图标。接下来，我们将创建一个演示事件用法的简单示例。最后，我们将看到小部件如何在wxWidgets应用程序中通信。\n\n/*------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/\nIconFrame.h\n\n    #ifndef ICONFRAME_ICONFRAME_H\n    #define ICONFRAME_ICONFRAME_H\n    \n    #include <wx/wx.h>\n    \n    class IconFrame : public wxFrame {\n    public:\n        IconFrame(const wxString& title);\n    };\n    \n    #endif //ICONFRAME_ICONFRAME_H\n/*------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/　\n\n\n/*------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/\nIconFrame.cpp\n\n    #include \"IconFrame.h\"\n    \n    IconFrame::IconFrame(const wxString &title)\n        :wxFrame(nullptr, wxID_ANY, title, wxDefaultPosition, wxSize(250, 150))\n    {\n        this->Center();\n    }\n/*------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/\n\n\n/*------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/　　　\nIconFrameApp.h\n\n    #ifndef ICONFRAME_ICONFRAMEAPP_H\n    #define ICONFRAME_ICONFRAMEAPP_H\n    \n    #include <wx/wx.h>\n    \n    class IconFrameApp : public wxApp {\n    public:\n        virtual bool OnInit();\n    };\n    \n    #endif //ICONFRAME_ICONFRAMEAPP_H\n/*------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/\n\n\n/*------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/\nIconFrameApp.cpp\n\n    #include \"IconFrameApp.h\"\n    #include \"IconFrame.h\"\n    \n    wxIMPLEMENT_APP(IconFrameApp);\n    \n    bool IconFrameApp::OnInit() {\n        IconFrame *frame = new IconFrame(wxT(\"Icon Frame\"));\n        frame->Show(true);\n    \n        return true;\n    }\n/*------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/","edit_time_ms":1658489757639,"title":"图标窗口程序","snapshots":[],"char_count":{"word":177,"char_without_spaces":1774,"char_with_spaces":2008}}